item.description:
Liz, Judi, and I met up with Robin and went on a little walk in her woods today with our dogs and it looks like a nice place for a meetup. No major hills or swampy areas (one or two spots where the dogs can get wet though) from what we saw.

Anyone interested please join Beau and I as we explore the new area with Robin and her lab Shemp. Make sure to bring poop bags so we can keep the trail clean.

If you come via 101, take exit 3 and then it's about 7 miles and 4 turns off the exit.

group.name: Human Soles & Doggie Paws Hikers & Walkers of Manchester, NH
